Rich:

    I don't know if this skill exists or not, but if it doesn't, it should.
 :)

    Rationale:  there's no way to make opium dealing work without it.
 Especially opium dealing as an attack upon a taxing lord's realm.  I noticed
that nobody was selling opium on the recent money report.  

    If this skill were to make thieves too powerful, perhaps we could develop
another skill to track thieves, thus bringing counter-intelligence to the
game. :)

------------------------------------------------------
95??  Fencing, a hidden skill under stealth

Use of this skill allows a thief to buy and sell items on the market
anonymously.  Buy and sell orders will appear publically as "a fence" or
something like that.


-Dave

