Rich, for my g2 wish list (and g1, as well...).

Can we please,please,please,please have some modifications to the admit
permissions system (and faction relations in general).

I just got burned *again*, because a friend of mine couldn't move into
my tower.  It's really kind-of silly for us to have to do all these
"admit x00 j9j j9j j9j..." orders, when something like
"ally j9j j9j j9j" would do everything that I would like (and more).

Thanks for making such a wonderful game!

Ed "I'm a landowner :)" Bailey
