Status: RO

This problem (units attacking friendly units for which they have DEFEND
status) has certainly been around for a long time.  I remember
discussions about it on turn 2.  If I were writing the game I would
ensure that a unit never attacks another unit which it would defend.
But Rich wasn't persuaded of the value of this change.

                                        David desJardins

